    <h1>Top Urologist Warns: Every Month You Spend In "Watchful Waiting" Mode, Your Bladder Is Quietly Turning To Scar Tissue — And Most Men Have No Idea Until It's Too Late To Reverse</h1>

    <div class="byline-box">
      <div class="byline-ava">
        {%- if section.settings.doctor_image != blank -%}
