      <p>✅ <strong>Smooth muscle relaxation via the nitric oxide pathway</strong> — releases the grip on the urethra so the bladder can finally empty without straining</p>
    </div>

    <p>The specific combination that delivers all three: <strong>lipidosterolic saw palmetto extract and pumpkin seed oil.</strong></p>

    <p>Saw palmetto in its properly extracted oil form is a well-studied 5-alpha-reductase inhibitor. Pumpkin seed oil delivers both anti-inflammatory plant sterols and arginine — the natural precursor to the nitric oxide signal that tells smooth muscle to release tension.</p>

    <p>Together, they address the obstruction from two directions. That's the difference between managing a symptom and actually changing what the bladder has to work against every night.</p>


